<title>GSettings Schemas</title>

<p>
Projects that use GSettings for configuration storage need to <link xref="installing">install</link> a schema file into a system location.
The schemas need to be listed using the <code>data|gsettings|schemas</code> <link xref="variables">variable</link>.
</p>
<example>
<p>
For example, this <link xref="recipe-files">recipe</link> specified one schema to be installed:
</p>
<code>
data|gsettings|schemas = org.example.Example.gschema.xml
</code>
</example>
